  <span id="freeText5460177073858973558" style="display:none">This book is inspiring and heart breaking because you learn so much from this book. It's about a young girl named Nujood who loves going to school and loves being with her family, she lives in a country called Yemen where you are forced to get married before 15 . One day she comes home from school and her dad tells she will soon get married. She is heart broken because her wedding will be coming soon. After her wedding Nujood struggled with her new " husband" she now lives with and his family . Later during their marriage her husband let her go see her parents and visit them for awhile and that's when she gets the courage to go to court and demand a divorce. I love how Nujood toke courage to get what she wanted and also worked hard for it. I would recommend this book to my friends or others. </span>
