  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/374024967?book_show_action=true">Jul 21, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lisa" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lisa" href="/user/show/2232612-lisa">Lisa</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer374024967" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3898224544789381527">“I’m a simple village girl who has always obeyed the orders of my father and brothers. Since forever, I have learned to say yes to everything. Today I have decided to say no.”<br/><br/>Good story which takes place in Yemen and is the story of 10-year old Nujood Ali who was forced by her father to marry a man who was three times her age. She was made to go live with her husband and his family, was raped by her husband, and was emotionally and physically abused by his mother. Yemeni law allows girls of any </span>
  <span id="freeText3898224544789381527" style="display:none">“I’m a simple village girl who has always obeyed the orders of my father and brothers. Since forever, I have learned to say yes to everything. Today I have decided to say no.”<br /><br />Good story which takes place in Yemen and is the story of 10-year old Nujood Ali who was forced by her father to marry a man who was three times her age. She was made to go live with her husband and his family, was raped by her husband, and was emotionally and physically abused by his mother. Yemeni law allows girls of any age to wed, but it forbids sex with them until an indefinite time when they are considered "suitable for sexual intercourse."<br /><br />She fled to the courthouse at the capitol, which was extremely gutsy for a 10-year old, let alone a girl. What Nujood did helped to change an archaic system that allowed young girls to be married while underage. Internationally it created a fire storm which then helped to change this custom in Yemen and other Middle Eastern countries. In November 2008, Glamour magazine designated Nujood Ali and her lawyer Shada Nasser as Women of the Year.<br /><br />This is a book we all should read to see what some women in the world go through in their day to day lives. Most of us who will be reading this book, do not have to go through this. By reading this book, maybe one of us can help someone by reaching out a hand to help in some small way.<br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="3898224544789381527" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

